2002, she entered Beijing Film Academy and spent four years there.\n\n==Career==\nIn March 2008, Bo joined a group of eight other writers to script a remake of \"Dream of Red Mansions\". Three months later, the \"youthful dream team\" had finished 50 drafts. Bonnie was responsible for eight scenes.\n\n==Filmography==\n*\"Flea on the drum when the move\" (screenwriter)\n*\"Prodigal Yan Qing\" (screenwriter)\n*\"Loess Ballad\" (screenwriter)\n*New version of \"Dream of Red Mansions\" (writer)\n*The movie \"Mulan\" (screenwriter)\n*\"Like love you like Bonnie 'essays\n*\"Not luxury\", \"false\" celebrity interviews set\n\n==External links==\n*{{cite web|url=http://baike.baidu.com/view/1552981.htm |title=\u67cf\u90a6\u59ae_\u767e\u5ea6\u767e\u79d1 |publisher=Baike.baidu.com |date=2012-02-24 |accessdate=2012-05-29}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://women.sohu.com/20080702/n257880570_4.shtml |title=\u72ec\u5bb6\u91c7\u8bbf\uff1a\u5486\u54ee\u5973\u90ce\u67cf\u90a6\u59ae-\u641c\u72d0\u5973\u4eba |publisher=Women.sohu.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-29}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.kaixin001.com/diary/view_65218987_29840495.html |title=\u65b0\u7248\u300a\u7ea2\u697c\u68a6\u300b\u4e3b\u529b\u7f16\u5267\u67cf\u90a6\u59ae:\u9000\u5b66\u7684\u9ad8\u8003\u72b6\u5143 - \u300a\u610f\u6797\u300b\u7684\u65e5\u8bb0 - \u5f00\u5fc3\u7f51 |publisher=Kaixin001.com |date=2010-03-26 |accessdate=2012-05-29}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.tianshannet.com.cn/special/banlv/200907/2009-07/30/content_4364987.htm |title=\u67cf\u90a6\u59ae\uff1a\u50cf38D\u4e00\u6837\u9a84\u50b2\u5730\u751f\u6d3b - \u65b0\u7586\u5929\u5c71\u7f51 |publisher=Tianshannet.com.cn |date=2009-07-30 |accessdate=2012-05-29}}\n*{{cite web|author=\u8ddf\u8d34\u533a |url=http://news.163.com/10/0723/09/6C93COF900014AEE.html |title=\u7f16\u5267\u67cf\u90a6\u59ae\uff1a\u5174\u9ad8\u91c7\u70c8\u5954\u8dd1\u7684\u516b\u5341\u540e(\u56fe)_\u7f51\u6613\u65b0\u95fb\u4e2d\u5fc3 |publisher=News.163.com |date=2010-05-29 |accessdate=2012-05-29}}\n*{{